name: Tonya Brandon
text:
Amazing place of rest and revelation in the Holy Spirit!
Cal & Jewell are amazing hosts who minister with such depth and joy!
One amazing retreat location for groups and individuals. Definite 5 stars!! We will be returning! ❤️💙💜

name: Robert Melvin
text: If you're looking for a good old country church, full of the holy spirit and non judgemental people, this is the place to be on Sundays at 11:00.
